.TH "__batadv_mcast_mla_update" 9 "__batadv_mcast_mla_update" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
__batadv_mcast_mla_update \- update the own MLAs
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" __batadv_mcast_mla_update
.BI "(struct batadv_priv *bat_priv "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bat_priv" 12
the bat priv with all the soft interface information
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Updates the own multicast listener announcements in the translation
table as well as the own, announced multicast tvlv container.

Note that non-conflicting reads and writes to bat_priv->mcast.mla_list
in \fBbatadv_mcast_mla_tt_retract\fP and \fBbatadv_mcast_mla_tt_add\fP are
ensured by the non-parallel execution of the worker this function
belongs to.
